Title: Checks need to be spreaded more over time
Component: core
State: open
Date: 2014-12-12 09:04:53
Targetversion: future
Class: bug

A common case is when a user enables the Check_MK Discovery service or
reschedules all of them at once. Then the services seem to be checked near
to eachother which might result in unneccessary load peaks.  It would be
much better to spread the checks more over time.

Lösung: Im Multisite stellen wir das Formular mit den Aktionen so um,
dass automatisch über mehr Zeit verteilt wird.
